eu.h2020.symbiote.rpcserver

Class RestAPICallback<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.h2020.symbiote.rpcserver.RestAPICallback<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.util.concurrent.FailureCallback, org.springframework.util.concurrent.ListenableFutureCallback<T>, org.springframework.util.concurrent.SuccessCallback<T>

    public class RestAPICallback<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.util.concurrent.ListenableFutureCallback<T>

    A Callback for listening to REST replies asynchronously

    This class extends the ListenableFutureCallback class and manually sends back the HTTP reply it receives to the specified "reply-To" queue of the RabbitMQ request received by the RPCServers.
    Since:
    2017-01-26
